Whoops, forgot about ol' KitKat2.

::FZ::

FZ approaches the entrance to the Iron Fist (which, by the way, is on 
an island 3 miles off of the coast of Spain), seeing KitKat there. He 
knew from Zardus's mind that she had been sent to take over her pack 
again.

"Why are you back here?" he asks, coming up behind her.




--- In nbwrpg@y..., logomorph@h... wrote:
> ::KitKat2::
> 
> She sighed and said sarcastically at the entrance of the Allience 
> base,"Ha  Ha  Ha  Ha. Very funny guys. I'm laughing so hard, I'll 
> just bust a gasket. Now let me in. It's not funny anymore."
> 
> She sat on her hind legs and waited.
